://lihkg.com/thread/1685616</a><br />\n大一海鮮火鍋被手足踢爆咗係藍扮黃<br />\n<br />\n罪行一: 明明深藍股東凌以徽(紅會 香港菁英會執委)同譚思略(鼎爺私房菜大股東) 仲係大一嘅董事 (好彩俾手足發現造假，請到前post <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/17\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/17</a> #408, <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/18\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/18</a> #426<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/20\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678200/page/20</a> #477) 但大一就聲稱深藍股東已經退咗股，凌以徽仲曾經話手足智障添，不過俾人篤爆，真係唔知邊個智障嘞<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGPt9SF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGPt9SF.jpg&h=4105d1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪行二: 消費FA，請問有邊隊FA咁山寨，出嚟講兩句吖，扮FA咁狗都做得出<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjOuUjt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjOuUjt.png&h=e545ada3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪行三: 俾手足踢爆深藍凌以徽仲係大一董事之後，連Del. 兩個扮黃post. 分別係扮FA果個，仲有一個係呼籲手足上去大一海鮮火鍋休息，極具篤灰意味!<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahb00Zz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fahb00Zz.png&h=331da6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪行四 (手足報料) (20191102 追加): 由第一個踢爆post開始，佢哋冇諗過出嚟大方承認，反而選擇鬼祟掩飾。深藍凌以徽嘅私家擺相位仲攞嚟做連儂牆，啲字跡仲要張張差唔多，真係對連儂牆嘅一大侮辱! <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqFk0ZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqFk0ZM.png&h=2e412eb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACDR7EN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACDR7EN.jpg&h=b8c5b886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而凌以徽 徽徽同佢老豆凌冠華嘅其他惡行就喺晒下圖，包括但不限於奶共、扮黃、話手足係天使。除咗人渣之外都唔知點形容嘞。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k170gyg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk170gyg.jpg&h=b17a6304&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3nGLrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3nGLrC.jpg&h=5e3ca6f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPKNFZX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPKNFZX.jpg&h=19001f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深藍凌氏家族除咗大一之外仲有間叫茶王冰室(有旺角同中環兩間分店)都係姓凌嘅打骰，茶王冰室董事長係廢老凌冠華，沖茶師傅梁東坡係凌冠華女婿。而凌冠華曾經喺東方日報度做，識好多報紙編輯。姓凌兩父子仲有間公司叫PR Asia，據報啲正評都係佢哋PR公司買返嚟。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZS1oYM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZS1oYM3.png&h=4461f3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n茶王有個所謂黃絲股東叫陳佰勤，咁應該點呀? 我諗咗好耐，覺得無論如何都唔應該俾啲深藍賤人食手足嘅人血饅頭，而且係極深藍! 同埋點解明知姓凌嘅係深藍都會痴埋去呢? 中環果間分店11月先開張噃，反送中都成5個月啦，咁都唔割蓆。所以都覺得呢位陳生都唔係咁忠實嘅黃絲啫，都呼籲佢回頭是岸，咪再痴埋去班藍屍度嘞。<br />\n<br />\n我出呢個post 主力係要打擊藍扮黃，藍滲入黃嘅食店，而大一火鍋料理同茶王冰室斷得咁正，絶對係一個指標嚟，究竟我哋應該點對呢類藍扮黃嘅鋪頭絶對會影響之後嘅風氣。<br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲大家可以繼續話俾其他人聽，大一同茶王都有極深藍嘅成員喺度，可以繼續去作出以下行動<br />\n<br />\n1.  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">食環戰線</span></strong> 食環署24小時熱線2868 0000<br />\n手足報料<br />\ni. 中環中心茶王冰室係拎食物工廠牌<br />\n唔可以放櫈同坐客食野嫁<br />\n<br />\nii. 直至11月1號<br />\n中環中心茶王冰室都係無牌經營<br />\n<br />\n2.  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Social media 戰線</span></strong><br />\n入去俾嬲同俾大家知道兩間都係扮黃閪鋪<br />\n<br />\n大一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/daiichihotpot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdaiichihotpot&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=d57504e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/daiichihotpot</a><br />\n茶王<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CafeTeaMaster/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCafeTeaMaster%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=41986252\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CafeTeaMaster/</a><br />\n<br />\n3.  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃藍戰線</span></strong><br />\n投票大一火鍋係藍屍:<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2Fdirects%2F587&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=04bd4d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/587</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/5685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2Fdirects%2F5685&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=20b376b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/5685</a><br />\n<br />\n投票茶王冰室係藍屍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/2232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2Fdirects%2F2232&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=cf5b71b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/directs/2232</a> 旺角分店<br />\n<br />\n中環分店仲未有link，我會去報料，有link 再俾大家<br />\n<br />\n再去埋黃藍地圖報料: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ%2Fviewform&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=deea71d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n追擊黃扮藍閪鋪，我哋責無旁貸!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"sor.  最尾果句應該係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>藍扮黃</strong></span>先啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f2573e97824f9f83f655e2d2f03a6a0ceeac68","tid":1693421,"uid":247048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"曱近平推下先"},{"pid":"2649e2b8f5f3f38712e6e8ea0a2e5b8707ce3e7f","tid":1693421,"uid":43066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"都有成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src